#Text=Discover Your Unique Blueprint
#Text=What is a Blueprint ?
#Text=Formally , when people refer to a blueprint they associate it with a drawing ( a layout ) used to construct a design created by architects and/or engineers .
#Text=According to Wikipedia , “ the blue-print process was characterized by light colored lines on a blue background , a negative of the original .
#Text=The process was unable to reproduce color or shades of grey . ”
#Text=Less formally a blueprint is referred to simply as a plan .
#Text=Steps
#Text=In order for you to be able to distinguish a better life for yourself you have to recreate your plan and get rid of the grey areas in your life .
#Text=Creating a plan allows you to focus on the things that are important and it is virtually impossible to do if you are stuck in the grey areas of your life .
#Text=The grey areas in your life are thoughts of uncertainty , thoughts of worthlessness , thoughts of wanting to be successful but fearful .
#Text=Too often those grey areas are the blueprint of people ’s lives .
#Text=They plan their lives around what others think of them .
#Text=Now that you understand what blueprint you are working with , let ’s take a look at your life .
#Text=Evaluate areas in your life that need a plan .
#Text=I want you to write down or type as many areas in your life that you feel could use a plan .

#Text=It could be your planning a vacation , living a healthier lifestyle , spending more time with family , starting a new business , whatever your area is write it down so you can hold yourself accountable for it .
#Text=Now , write down the why .
#Text=Why do you need to create a plan for that vacation ?
#Text=It could be you just spontaneously decided to go to Jamaica but you have n’t saved up for it .
#Text=Living a healthier lifestyle , you ’ve been putting it off for weeks , months , maybe years .
#Text=You know you ’ve been wanting to do it but do n’t have a plan of execution .
#Text=Last but not least , you ’ve been wanting to go after your passion and your dreams but do n’t have a plan of execution .
#Text=You ’ve conducted a ton of research , attended hundreds of networking events , made great contacts but you are not taking any action .
#Text=Why not ?
#Text=Could it be you are paralyzed by the fear of success ?
#Text=Fear of success , what does that mean exactly ?
#Text=The fear of success is wanting to go after a desire but afraid of the process .
#Text=Some people believe they do n’t have the right to be successful .
#Text=They live their lives with the thought of being mediocre is sufficient .
#Text=They remain in the shadows of other people ’s successes .
#Text=Well what if you gave success a try ?
#Text=You could not only see but reap the benefits of going after your heart ’s desire .
#Text=Tips
#Text=So let ’s summarize it this way , basically a blueprint is a plan that is derived from , characterized from , a negative of the original and unable to reproduce shades of grey .
#Text=Interesting right ?
#Text=So , if your life was like a blueprint , you should what , recreate yourself from your original self , produce a plan that is unable to reproduce any shades of grey .
#Text=Warnings
#Text=Most people hold back , afraid to take chances , afraid to step out into their greatness .
#Text=It ’s not that they did n’t have goals and dreams everybody wants more .
#Text=When something happens to them they began to believe that ’s the way it is and they do n’t know how to change it .
#Text=So what do they do , they keep you from yours .
#Text=Just keep moving forward and stop caring what others think about your dreams .
#Text=You have to do what is right for you .
#Text=Do n’t let that be your story .
#Text=Create your own story , create your own future .
#Text=Where are you going with your life ?
#Text=What is your Why ?
#Text=Why do you do what you do ?
#Text=What moves you ?
#Text=What drives you ?
#Text=What makes you want to be better ?
#Text=What is the purpose behind what you want to do ?
#Text=Who are you doing this for ?
#Text=These are the questions that you have to ask yourself .
#Text=You have to find your why and when you find your why , why you want to be successful then you have to find a way to make it happen .
#Text=When you find your why you will decide you do n’t have an option to quit .
#Text=When you find your why you will find that you are in charge of your destiny .
#Text=Find out your why and go after it like your life depends on it .
#Text=Like you are running for your life .
